Class OgmQueryTranslatorFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hibernate.ogm.query.impl.OgmQueryTranslatorFactory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    QueryTranslatorFactory

    public class OgmQueryTranslatorFactory
extends Object
implements QueryTranslatorFactory
    Creates QueryTranslators. Depending on whether the underlying datastore supports queries itself, a translator executing native queries or a translator executing Lucene queries via Hibernate Search will be created.
